rows.label: qst200317_msg0001
rows.name: Oh! It's you lot!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0002
rows.name: I saved them all. They are safe!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0003
rows.name:
Thank you! You're a good
guy, despite your looks.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0004
rows.name:
But... I let the Gogol
escape. I am sorry.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0005
rows.name: The Gogol?

rows.label: qst200317_msg0006
rows.name:
Actually, the rockfall was the work
of a Gogol. But it got away...

rows.label: qst200317_msg0007
rows.name: Hey, are you serious?!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0008
rows.name:
A Gogol just appeared in the city
and went on a huge rampage!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0009
rows.name: What?!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0010
rows.name: Are you sure?

rows.label: qst200317_msg0011
rows.name:
Yeah, I'm sure. It attacked
the workers nearby...

rows.label: qst200317_msg0012
rows.name:
It grabbed a woman, climbed the
tower, and let out a huge roar...

rows.label: qst200317_msg0013
rows.name:
It was total chaos, I tell you. Luckily
the Luxurian army drove it off quickly,
so the damage was minimal...

rows.label: qst200317_msg0014
rows.name:
What gives? It pretended to
run, then attacked the city?!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0015
rows.name:
Mmm, unforgivable! I will
absolutely... catch the Gogol!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0016
rows.name: ...Wait a moment, Jikarao.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0017
rows.name: ...Hm? Are we not going to catch it?!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0018
rows.name:
What is it, Meleph? Did
something catch your attention?

rows.label: qst200317_msg0019
rows.name: Hmm... Something doesn't add up.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0020
rows.name:
The Gogol fled in a direction
away from the city. And it
didn't climb the pillar.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0021
rows.name:
No matter how fast it is,
could it really have attacked
the city from there?

rows.label: qst200317_msg0024
rows.name:
Indeed... It might be best
to investigate a little.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0025
rows.name:
Jikarao, before we go catch
the Gogol, let's talk to
the people in the city.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0026
rows.name: ...Mmm.
